== English ==
=== Etymology ===
From ''[[jocular]]'' + ''[[ly]]''.
=== Adverb ===
'''jocularly'''
# In a [[jocular]] manner; [[humourously]].
#: ''He was in such a good mood that he even managed to take out the rubbish '''jocularly'''.''

